	("Holo Grenade, Mk 1", "Grenades 1-H", 1, 50, 0, 20, 0, drawn, 0, "L", "explode (10.; see text)", ""Commonly used as novelties, holo grenades can create all sorts of illusions in a harmless but surprising and often amusing way. A holo version of the wonder grenade (creating only an appearance of the listed effects) is popular among fey and children. However, holo grenades have less innocent uses as well0criminals and infiltrators use holo grenades as distractions.
